Package it.polimi.ingsw.shared.RemoteInterfaces

Interface ClientRemote

All Superinterfaces:
Remote, Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:
ClientModel
All Known Implementing Classes:
ClientModelCLI, ClientModelGUI
public interface ClientRemote extends Remote, Serializable
This object is used on the client to receive updates sent by the model. This object will be wrapped inside a ClientRMI object. The server, inside ClientRMI, will invoke methods on this object and the remote execution will be handled by RMI. Please note that the interface is superfluous, but it's needed by RMI to work properly.
